This place is the same.

15
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,840
Although five years passed already.

16
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,560
- Jeong Dae Hyeon— 
 - You became famous.

17
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,540
I saw the news.

18
00:02:02,180 --> 00:02:04,110
You even have a girlfriend.

19
00:02:04,110 --> 00:02:06,290
- Dae Hyeon— 
 - But does that woman know?

20
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:09,810
That she's dating only a shell, who's a fake?

21
00:02:09,810 --> 00:02:12,120
I'm getting married.

22
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:15,650
I don't want to explain myself to you about what happened back then.

23
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:17,490
Stop coming to me like this and

24
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:20,030
stop fixing these things for me.

25
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:23,760
You should also focus on your happiness and move on.

26
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:26,560
I've been thinking about this all the way here.

27
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:31,560
What am I trying to do by going to see someone I'm done with?

28
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,810
I think I know now.

29
00:02:33,810 --> 00:02:35,570
Lee Do Han,

30
00:02:35,570 --> 00:02:38,260
it looks like...

31
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:41,150
I want to scar you.

32
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:43,570
So, I'm going to give it a try.

33
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:47,370
While only focusing on my happiness.

